comments: Melton (PHI) brushes Butler's (MIA) arm and the contact on the perimeter is marginal.
Adebayo (MIA) and Embiid (PHI) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Vincent (MIA) extends his arm forward and makes contact with Harden's (PHI) arm as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Melton (PHI) is moving alongside Vincent's (MIA) path and marginal body contact occurs in transition.
Tucker (PHI) is moving alongside Butler's (MIA) path and avoids making contact with his left arm as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) jumps vertically and absorbs the marginal contact from Butler (MIA) as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Martin (MIA) immediately slides his hand off of Melton's (PHI) side and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Melton (PHI) is already in Martin's (MIA) path and he absorbs the contact.
Martin (MIA) maintains verticality and marginal contact occurs with Harden (PHI) during his shot near the rim.
Martin (MIA) and Harden (PHI) briefly engage and disengage as they pursue the rebound.
Herro (MIA) briefly grasps Harden's (PHI) arm and marginal contact occurs as Harden secures the loose ball.
Martin (MIA) comes to, but not through, Harden's (PHI) space, making hand contact to the ball as Harden stands up.
Harden (PHI) falls out of bounds with the ball in his possession. The possession is correctly given to Miami.
Adebayo (MIA) is already in Tucker's (PHI) path and he absorbs the contact.
Embiid (PHI) is moving alongside Butler's (MIA) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Butler (MIA) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot and he moves his pivot foot after his gather.
Melton (PHI) is already in Adebayo's (MIA) path when contact occurs and he absorbs the contact.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in Martin's (MIA) path and does not deliver contact.
Embiid (PHI) is already in Vincent's (MIA) path and absorbs the contact as he releases away from Vincent.
Adebayo (MIA) is moving alongside Embiid's (PHI) path and marginal body contact occurs during Embiid's drive.
Adebayo (MIA) cleanly blocks Embiid's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Melton (PHI) and Herro (MIA) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Martin (MIA) establishes himself in Tucker's (PHI) path and marginal contact occurs as Tucker commits to going under the pick.
Martin (MIA) is already in Tucker's (PHI) path and is firming up over his right foot when contact occurs.
Harden (PHI) moves forward into Butler's (MIA) lower body and initiates contact that affects Butler's follow-through.
Martin (MIA) and Tucker (PHI) briefly engage and immediately disengage during rebounding.
Adebayo (MIA) places his hand momentarily on Embiid's (PHI) side and marginal contact occurs during the inbound.
Adebayo (MIA) brings his hand toward Embiid's (PHI) side and marginal contact occurs during Embiid's drive.
Butler (MIA) legally contests Harden's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
